Ability Construction Reflection API
Mapper class makes a map of all public constructors without @ommittedConstructor in elements/* and ability/* folders of C-Engine and DC-Engine.
[known to fail if full path contains Russian letters!]

From XML, e.g.
<Abilities>
<ActiveAbility>
<SelectiveTargeting><Conditions>
<StringComparison><STRING>{MATCH_TYPE}</STRING><STRING>TERRAIN</STRING></StringComparison>
</Conditions></SelectiveTargeting>
<Effects><SummonEffect><STRING>^VAR</STRING></SummonEffect></Effects>
</ActiveAbility>
</Abilities>

To construct an Abilities object,

Argument types

Primitives - String, Int, Boolean


Each Active (Spell, Action, Quick Item Active) has Abilities.




